				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Download from the Google Play Store on your Andro</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">id </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">smartphone</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> (OS 2.1 or above) –</span>
			</p>
			<ol type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">On your phone, select the Google Play Store. </span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Search for “7by24.” Choose “7by24” from the results, click Install” button so the app will automatically install.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Choose “Accept &amp; Download. There will be no charge,</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">since the 7by24 app is free.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Upon completion, the installed application will appear in your application drawer.</span>
				</li>
			</ol>
			<p style="margin-left:72pt; line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.003.jpg" width="351" height="220" alt="" />
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<a href="#OnlineManualAndroidSetup"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Go to Android 7by24 App Setup</span></a><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><br /><a href="#OnlineManualTop"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Return to top of Online User Manual</span></a>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<a name="OnlineManualiOSSetup"></a><strong><u><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">7by24 App </span></u></strong><strong><u><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Setup</span></u></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">For the </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">iPhone</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">/</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">iOS</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> app:</span>
			</p>
			<ol type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Register your mobile phone number at an authorized 7by24 retailer.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Choose the 7by24 app icon to start the setup.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">When you open the 7by24 app for </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">the first time, you will reach </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">the activation screen.</span>
				</li>
			</ol>
			<p style="margin-left:72pt; line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.004.jpg" width="121" height="211" alt="" />
			</p>
			<ol start="4" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Enter your registered mobile phone number in a local format (e.g. if you are in the US, select the US flag and enter in your 10-digit number) and press the ‘send’ button </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">(i.e., the paper airplane symbol).</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">A text message will be sent to the mobile phone number you entered, containing the 4-digit activation code. Enter it in the appropriate field and press the ‘Send’ button (i.e., the paper airplane symbol).</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">If you do not receive the text message within one minute, press ‘I never got the code’. The system will then call you and deliver the code over a phone call.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Wait for the activation confirmation window and you will access the application.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">At this point you will reach the main screen of the application, </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">w</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">ith access to the </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Dialpad</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Wait for the ‘status’ icon to be green in the settings section</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">(indicating that the application is connected properly to your network) and you are good to go.</span>
				</li>
			</ol>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<a href="#OnlineManualTop"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Return to top of Online User Manual</span></a>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<a name="OnlineManualAndroidSetup"></a><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">For the Android app:</span>
			</p>
			<ol type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Register your mobile phone number at an authorized 7by24 retailer.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Choose the 7by24 app icon to start the setup.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">When you open the 7by24 app for the first time, you will reach the </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">activation screen.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Enter your registered mobile phone number in a local format (e.g. if you </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">are in the US, select the US flag and enter in your 10-digit number) </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">and press the ‘send’ button (i.e., the paper airplane symbol).</span>
				</li>
			</ol>
			<p style="margin-left:72pt; line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.005.jpg" width="110" height="196" alt="" style="border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.75pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.75pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-bottom-color:#000000" />
			</p>
			<ol start="5" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Review the pop up message and confirm you entered the number </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">correctly.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">A text message will be sent to the mobile phone number you entered, </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">containing the 4-digit activation code. Enter it in the appropriate </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">field and press the ‘Send’ button (i.e., the paper airplane symbol).</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">If you do not receive the text message within one minute, press ‘I never got the code’. </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">The system will then call you and deliver the code over a phone call.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Wait for the activation confirmation window. You will be then able </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">to now access the application.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:67.34pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:4.66pt; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">At this point you will reach the main screen of the application – the </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Dialpad</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">.</span>
				</li>
			</ol>
			<p style="margin-left:72pt; line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.006.jpg" width="158" height="193" alt="" />
			</p>
			<ol start="10" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
				<li style="margin-left:72pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Wait for the “7by24” app to be properly connected to the Internet </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">and ready for use - the ‘7by24’ icon in your notification bar will by colored, </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">rather than grayed out.</span>
				</li>
			</ol>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<a href="#OnlineManualTop"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Return to top of Online User Manual</span></a><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<a name="OnlineManualProfile"></a><strong><u><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">My Profile</span></u></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">You can control how others see you in their 7by24 interface. The Profile section also allows you to see your phone number for which the 7by24 app is registered. All other Profile settings are completely optional.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">To display your profile, from the top menu, choose</span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.007.jpg" width="24" height="21" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> to reach a list of “Options”. Choose the </span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.008.jpg" width="29" height="27" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">“My Profile” button.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.009.jpg" width="144" height="215" alt="iPhone My Profile.png" />
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Select the</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.010.jpg" width="21" height="21" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">button to either attach a new or existing image to your profile.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Y</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">ou may set a unique ID and email, if you wish.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">The dialogue balloon pointing to the profile image</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">(marked in the image as “I am using 7by24!”) is the default text shown for your status and can be changed.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<a href="#OnlineManualTop"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Return to top of Online User Manual</span></a><br /><strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">&#xa0;</span></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<a name="OnlineManualDialing"></a><strong><u><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Dialing a 7by24 Call</span></u></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">7by24 can work both on your data plan (3G, 4G, </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">LTE</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">) or over </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Wifi</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">. </span><br /><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Before you make a call, make sure that your device uses your preferred connection type for the call. If your data plan is not unlimited, using Wi-Fi is always the best way to avoid additional charges from your mobile provider.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Once you set up the app, after you open the application, the </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">dialpad</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> will be in front of you. You can then dial the destination normally and touch the green ‘Call’ button icon at the bottom.</span><br /><br /><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.011.jpg" width="163" height="288" alt="7by24 Dialpad.PNG" style="border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.75pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.75pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-bottom-color:#000000" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">[Note – For Android phones only, y</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">ou can whether the app is properly connected </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">to the Internet</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> and ready for use</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> by making sure that the 7by24</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> icon </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">in</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> your Android notification bar is colored, rather than grayed out.</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">]</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">When the app is properly connected, your 7by24 account balance should be listed in the lower left corner. </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">To call an international destination (any country other than the U.S.) dial “011” or “+” or “00” and then the country code and number. For calling U.S. numbers, you can dial using only the 10-digit number </span><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">or “1” plus the 10 digit number.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">The backspace button</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> deletes the last digit entered.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">When you are finished entering the number, press the “Call” button to dial. </span><br /><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">The display will switch to a Call view. When they answer, your call will enjoy 7by24’s everyday low intern</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">ational and domestic per minute</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> rates.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Press the big red button at the bottom of the Call view to hang up.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<a href="#OnlineManualTop"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Return to top of Online User Manual</span></a><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<a name="OnlineManualContactList"></a><strong><u><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Connecting Through Your Contact List</span></u></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">To access your Contact list, touch the Contacts icon</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.012.jpg" width="25" height="24" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">from the upper menu. </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">7by24 app’s Contacts list can display not only all your contacts, but should also identify which contacts have the 7by24 app installed and registered on their device. </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">When both you and your registered 7by24 contact are online and connect through the 7by24 app, your 7by24 call or instant message is free.*</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Within 7by24 Contacts, the bottom menu allows you to select several different views of your contacts as well as add or modify a contact: All. 7by24 registered app users, or favorites. The bottom menu option with a “+” will enable you to add a contact. (Note – Any contact addition or edits made via 7by24 will also change your main device’s Contact information.)</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">To find a contact within the various Contacts views, you can either scroll down/up to </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">the  desired</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> contact , tap the first letter of the last name, or type in their name in the upper search field. Again, if a ‘7by24’ logo is next to the contact’s name, it means that they have 7by24 app installed and registered, so when they are also online you can reach them through their 7by24 app for free either for a voice call, </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">video call or </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">instant message.</span><a href="#OnlineManual3"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:6.67pt; vertical-align:super">3</span></a>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">You will enjoy 7by24’s everyday low rates for all other calls (e.g.</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">,  to</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> your other contacts and offline 7by24 app users). Touch the desired contact to access the specific contact details.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<a href="#OnlineManualTop"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Return to top of Online User Manual</span></a><br /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<a name="OnlineManualConnectNotRegistered"></a><strong><u><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Connecting with Your Contacts Not Registered with 7by24</span></u></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">For connecting to contact’s who are not registered with 7by24, you make a voice call to them through the 7by24 app using 7by24’s everyday low rates – available for international and domestic voice calls. </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">7by24 calls require that you have access to your 3G/4G/LTE </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">data plan or a </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Wifi</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> connection.</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:6.67pt; vertical-align:super">1</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">The contact detail view lists a single phone number. If there are several phone numbers saved under the same contact, slide the screen sideways to browse between the numbers.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.013.jpg" width="140" height="248" alt="7by24 Basic Contact Details.PNG" style="border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.75pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.75pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-bottom-color:#000000" />
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">You can edit the contact by touching at the bottom edit contact button next to the Favorites star.  To mark as a favorite, touch the star. Any edits you make will also apply to your device’s overall Contact List.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">[</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Note: </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">For Android phones only, t</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">o check </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">the per</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> minute </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">rate </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">for that number, under terms of your 7by24 c</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">alling plan, touch the Call “$”</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> button.</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> This function is presently unavailable and has been disabled on </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">iPhones</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> and </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">iOS</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> devices.]</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Press the </span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.014.jpg" width="18" height="15" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">blue receiver button to dial the call.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Note: The ability to send a message to</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> a contact to “Invite to 7by24”</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> or any SMS </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">are</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> currently </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">unavailable and disabled in the app.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<a href="#OnlineManualTop"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Return to top of Online User Manual</span></a>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<a name="OnlineManualConnectRegistered"></a><strong><u><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Connecting with Your Contacts Also Registered with 7by24</span></u></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">People in your Contact list that have the 7by24 app installed and registered on a phone or device are automatically flagged as 7by24 users, allowing you to contact them free of charge via </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">the app over 3G/4G/LTE or Wifi.</span><a href="#OnlineManual4"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:6.67pt; vertical-align:super">4</span></a><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">In your 7by24 Contact list, a 7by24 logo will appear next to their name to let you know which contacts are identified as 7by24 registered users.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">The app provides an Online status indicator on the registered 7by24 user’s image to show you whether the contact is available for a 7by24 call or not:</span>
			</p>
			<ul style="list-style-image:url('W:\Clients Proyects\7by24\CONTENT\7by24-online-user-manual-141024\7by24-online-user-manual-141024.015.png'); margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
				<li class="ListParagraph" style="margin-left:34.03pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:1.97pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">The contact is online and available for a call</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<ul style="list-style-image:url('W:\Clients Proyects\7by24\CONTENT\7by24-online-user-manual-141024\7by24-online-user-manual-141024.016.png'); margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
				<li class="ListParagraph" style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:33.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:2.75pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">The contact’s app is </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">turned  off</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> but they are available via Push (may take few more rings until they answer) but consumes much less battery.</span><br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both" />
				</li>
			</ul>
			<ul style="list-style-image:url('W:\Clients Proyects\7by24\CONTENT\7by24-online-user-manual-141024\7by24-online-user-manual-141024.017.png'); margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
				<li class="ListParagraph" style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:32.12pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:3.88pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">The contact is offline and cannot rece</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">ive a 7by24 call (you can still</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> call them at their phone number as a regular call, but at 7by24’s low everyday rates).</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.018.jpg" width="99" height="176" alt="" style="border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.75pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.75pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-bottom-color:#000000" />
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">From the Contact list, if they available via Push, touch the 7by24 logo next to it.</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> If they are available </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">o</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">nline, touch </span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.019.jpg" width="20" height="19" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">to m</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">ake a voice “Free Call,” </span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.020.jpg" width="15" height="15" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">to start a “Free Chat,” or</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.021.jpg" width="19" height="19" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> to make a video “Free Call.”</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:6.67pt; vertical-align:super"> </span><a href="#OnlineManual4"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:6.67pt; vertical-align:super">4</span></a>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.022.jpg" width="115" height="169" alt="iPhone Contact List Contact Details.png" />
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">You can also connect to them by touching the contact’s name itself to take you to the contact’s details. If they are online, you may press the corresponding “Free Call” and “Free Chat” buttons </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">to</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> connect.</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:6.67pt; vertical-align:super">4</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Whether they are online or offline you can also call them using the blue phone button; however, 7by24’s everyday low per minute rates will be applied to your account for this call.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<a href="#OnlineManualTop"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Return to top of Online User Manual</span></a>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<a name="OnlineManualCallFeatures"></a><strong><u><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">7by24 Call Features</span></u></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">While you are on a call, the following features</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> will be available for you</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">:</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Bluetooth</span></strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> – Allows you to use a Bluetooth earpiece or speaker instead of the default audio speaker/</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">mic</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">. This works automatically</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Mute</span></strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> – Mute your voice.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Dial Pad</span></strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> – Display the keypad.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Speaker</span></strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> – Use the loudspeaker and </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">mic</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Hold</span></strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> - Puts the call on hold. </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Instant Message</span></strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> – While on call, you may send and receive text, photos, audio and video files.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Video Call </span></strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">–Turn your voice call into a video call. The other party will have to approve the video request before the video session starts.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Additional options while on a call include</span><strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">:</span></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Add call</span></strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> – Make a conference call. The availability of this feature depends on your account type and calling plan. By default, this feature works only while you are on an incoming call.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Dial Pad </span></strong><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">– Display the keypad.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Note – Not all features are available for calls to contacts not registered with 7by24 or to offline contacts registered to 7by24.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<a href="#OnlineManualTop"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Return to top of Online User Manual</span></a>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<a name="OnlineManualRecentCallList"></a><strong><u><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Your 7by24 Recent Call List</span></u></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">To view your Rece</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">nt Call l List, touch </span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.023.jpg" width="24" height="24" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">when it appears in the screen’s upper menu.</span><br /><br /><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.024.jpg" width="162" height="288" alt="" style="border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.75pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.75pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-bottom-color:#000000" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">To call back a contact in the Recent Call list, touch the listing’s full entry. </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">To view the details of recent call to/from a specific contact, touch the right arrow in the entry. </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Note </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">–</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> In this recent call detai</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">ls, there you may also use the </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">options button in the upper right corner to make a voice call, video ca</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">ll or view the contact details.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">At the bottom of the recent call list, you can filter the list to display only missed calls or the entire list. </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">By pressing the bottom menu button of your phone additional options will be offered – View (determines whether to show all calls or only outgoing/incoming/missed); Total Duration (will calculate the total duration of the calls in the list); Delete All (will delete the recent call list).</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:11pt">
				<a href="#OnlineManualTop"><span class="Hyperlink" style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Return to top of Online User Manual</span></a>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<a name="OnlineManualReceivingCall"></a><strong><u><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt; ">Receiving a 7by24 Call</span></u></strong>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">For </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">the </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">iPhone</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">/</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">iOS</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> app</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">:</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">When you are connected to data either through your data plan or </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Wifi</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">, the app can send your device a notification of incoming calls, such as a banner, even when the phone is locked and its screen is turned off.</span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">Note </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">–</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> If you are not receiving any incoming call alerts, go to your </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">iOS</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> device Settings, select Notification Center, and choose the 7by24 app. There, you can adjust the alert style accordingly. </span>
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">In a locked screen, slide to answer.</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">You will then need to choose your calling type as explained below.</span>
			</p>
			<p>
				<img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.025.jpg" width="128" height="191" alt="iPhone Incoming Call Alert.png" /> <img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.026.jpg" width="126" height="188" alt="iPhone Income Call.png" />
			</p>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
				<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">When phone is unlocked and its screen turned on (when actively using the phone and its functions) or when the 7by24 app itself is open, an incoming call will display as a pop-up window:</span>
			</p>
			<ul type="square" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
				<li style="margin-left:27.58pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:8.42pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">To answer and start a vi</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">deo call immediately, touch the</span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.027.jpg" width="25" height="23" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">button. </span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:27.58pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:8.42pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">To answer and only start </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">a voice call, touch the</span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.028.jpg" width="25" height="23" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">button.</span>
				</li>
				<li style="margin-left:27.58pt; text-indent:0pt; line-height:115%; padding-left:8.42pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt">
					<span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">To reject the call touch the</span><img src="7by24-online-user-manual-141024/7by24-online-user-manual-141024.029.jpg" width="25" height="23" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:10pt">button.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p style="line-height:115%; font-size:10pt">
